name: Ghostville
description: "The girl's name is Harrya the ghost's name is Booo. She is walking on the street. There is lots of spots and there is a happy sun and two pumpkins and that has faces. The one has purple hair the other has blue hair with purple sprinkles and pompoms. The ghost has green hair with yellow streaks. I drew some lines in the tree to make it decorated and a lady bug is sitting in the tree. There is a polkadot heart and it is red and it is beautiful."
